snippet.title: April 27th | Five Nights at Freddy's: In Real Time
snippet.description:
Real Time Studio is a Five Nights at Freddy's fan-game team. Join us on Gamejolt or watch us here on YouTube!


Real Time Studio:
​⁠@Kabafmol - Animation
@TaarynIRT - Thumbnail / Video Editing

Music by:
@貴族音樂 - Topic

Even with our continuous effort working on Five Nights at Freddy's: In Real Time... to bring you guys the best game possible, we are delaying our release date until 'JUNE'. We've been working around the clock to bring you guys FNAF: In Real Time to life! But even us devs can't survive past 6 AM.

Can't wait to join the party... - Taaryn & Real Time Studio


Our collaborators form is up now! If you want to collaborate with us please fill out this form and we'll get back to you! https://forms.gle/gwyFvFYoLjzMkVRw7

Our social media links:
@RealTimeFNAF on all Platforms
(Instagram, Twitter, YouTube)

What is Five Nights at Freddy’s: In Real Time?
You work the nightshift at the soon to be closing Freddy Fazbear's Pizza, looking out for the animatronics now moving towards you in real time! Relive FNAF 1, and explore the story 10 years later with moving animatronics, new characters and storytelling. But, as we all know, the animatronics tend to wander a bit.

Why do I see all of these things?

Music:
Leon Riskin from FNAF World, Pizzeria Simulator and Sister Location.
Five Nights at Freddy’s by The Living Tombstone
Never Be Alone by Shadrow
Original Soundtrack by @TaarynIRT
